posting_body: ['The Fountains in the Park Apartments is nestled away in a beautiful setting with walking trails, yet conveniently close to the Twin Cities.', 'Our community has 1 and 2 bedroom apartments.', 'Fountains in the Park Apartments is located in the Central neighborhood of Brooklyn Park, MN with easy access to I-94 and I-694.', 'With oversized apartments, individual washer and dryer, private one stall garage included with rent, spacious balconies and ample closet space you will feel right at home here at The Fountains in the Park Apartments.', '-Ceiling Fans', '-Private Stall Garage w/remote', '-Dishwasher', '-On-Site Maintenance', '-Washer and Dryer in Unit', '-Balcony/Patio', '-Split Bathroom', '-Flex Rent Payments', '-Off', 'Street Parking', '-On-Site Management', '-Walk-in Closets', '-Gas Range', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Monday-Friday: 9AM-5PM', '5700 73rd Avenue North, Minneapolis, MN 55429', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Specials are based on availability and may expire or change at any time.', 'Specials and discounts may not be combined.', 'Rates are subject to change without advance notice.']
